org.happy.artist.rmdmia.rcsm
Interface RCSMInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
RCSMProvider, ROSNode
public interface RCSMInterface

The Robot Control System Messenger communication messaging interface/API between the Robot Hardware Controller and the Robotic Mission Decision Manager Intelligent Agent (RMDMIA).

setController

void setController(Controller controller)
The Controller ID is set automatically by the ControllerManager. Controller implementers of the RCSMProvider do not need to know anything about this method. Automatically set by the RCSMManager.

Parameters:
controller - the Controller of this instance of the RCSM.

initialize

void initialize()
                throws RCSMException
RCSM Provider initialization is called automatically by RCSMManager. Or manually via a RMDMIA Control Panel. Throws RCSMException as an Exception wrapper class for throwing Exceptions.

Throws:
RCSMException - an Exception wrapper class for throwing Exceptions.

isInitialized

boolean isInitialized()
Return boolean is initialized on RCSM Provider.

Returns:
boolean returns false if RCSM Provider is not initialized.

onInitialized

void onInitialized()
onInitialized is called by RCSMManager following all Provider initialization. Is implemented as abstract method and must be overridden to use in Provider implementation.

recycle

boolean recycle()
Recycle the RCSM Plugin back to its initialization state. without reinitializing the internal Objects (an Object reset switch). Returns true if provider was recycled.

Returns:
boolean true on success.

shutdown

void shutdown()
Shutdown the RCSM Plugin.
